ba_jail_indoorfun:

Always playig electric maps or damn copys of that?!? This time should be over.

The map contains cells with secrets and a door for throwing out weapons. The room is half dark like on mars maps.

Kind of othe stuff:

- Healing room in the middle of the top cells
- A armory with only 4 AWP's (thats really enough!)
- Map can be played without any Plugins! Weapons for Dgl Roulett or AWP unzoomed are there.
- Nice Disco with 6 Songs ans light effect.

Just download it, test it and if ou have suggestions pls add me in steam: anticheater1992 oder write me an E-Mail.

Thank a lot!
